{"tid":1336099,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Banner shop 蔡寶健 醉駕 法拉利 老婆 紅顏","createTime":"2019-07-20T19:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T02:44:53.000Z","uid":93479,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aa50fac1f16223de427d5b7d145ba80e029338dd","tid":1336099,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T19:13:32.000Z","msg":"老婆同二奶都好正<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n BannerSHOP老細蔡寶健（ Anthony），駕駛剛落地兩個月、價值逾四百多萬元的法拉利紅色跑車，接載國際青年商會香港總會靚女秘書長梁嘉恩（ Yoee），在中環皇后大道中遇到警方路障，蔡拒絕「吹波仔」外，還在現場大鬧一番。<br />\n<br />\n他更致電老婆到場幫拖，老婆立即阻擋記者採訪，擾攘一輪，卒之最後要勞煩警方及醫護人員夾手夾腳抬他上救護車。<br />\n<br />\n遇警查拒吹波　Banner王罰停牌<br />\n8男女庭外拉「天佑寶寶！唔腳痛！」橫額<br />\n2014-08-09<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140809/18826374\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140809%2F18826374&d=3A6Iqvk0VBPdaidkhJ82W5SOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=75f7e381\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140809%2F18826374&h=24d2cf05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140809/18826374</a><br />\n<br />\n法拉利醉男耍財技霸佔BannerSHOP!! <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140406/18680915\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140406%2F18680915&d=3A6Iqvk0VBPdaidkhJ82W5SOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=8f12ad8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140406%2F18680915&h=eae2f017\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140406/18680915</a><br />\n專門製作「易拉架」的BannerSHOP集團主席兼行政總裁蔡寶健，昨凌晨駕駛其法拉利紅色跑車，接載著名司儀梁嘉恩至中環時，途中因行車不穩，引起設置路障查酒駕的警員截查，惟蔡表現不合作，聲稱腳痛、抽筋、胃痛及有壓力，不肯提供酒精呼氣測試樣本，其妻聞訊趕至協助，蔡對妻說：「我好大壓力&hellip;&hellip;」，最終擾攘約一小時，蔡涉拒「吹波波」被捕。"},{"pid":"24ddd2960c38efcd8